import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, Container, Divider, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material';

export default function SenderConfig(): React.ReactElement {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth={'md'} sx={{ flex: 1, display: 'flex' }}>
      <Card sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
        <CardHeader title={'SenderConfig Settings'} />
        <Divider />
        <CardContent>
          <Grid container sx={{ flex: 1 }} direction="column">
            <Grid size={{ xs: 12 }}>
              <Typography sx={{ my: 3 }}> Email(SMTP)</Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={2} direction={'column'} alignItems={'center'}>
                <Grid>
                  Host:<></>
                </Grid>
                <Grid></Grid>
                <Grid></Grid>
                <Grid></Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
            <Grid size={{ xs: 12 }}>Sms</Grid>
            <Grid size={{ xs: 12 }}>save</Grid>
          </Grid>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  );
}
